OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FEnergy bills expected to   
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Ffall as new cap announced  
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Energy prices are expected to fall     
OL,6, sharply in April, with the regulator   
OL,7, Ofgem announcing its new price cap     
OL,8, later on Friday.                       
OL,10,FConsultancy Cornwall Insight has       
OL,11,Fpredicted a 14% drop, taking the       
OL,12,Ftypical annual bill to #1,656 - the    
OL,13,Flowest in more than two years.         
OL,15,FOfgem will make the announcement at    
OL,16,F07:00 GMT when it outlines the price   
OL,17,Fcap for April to June.                 
OL,19,FCampaigners say bills are still high   
OL,20,Fand many will struggle to pay.         
